Kintner and Lemoine regain Rotorua Crankworx pump track titles Friday, March 23, 2018 - 01:35 
Veteran pump track champions, Jill Kintner and Tomas Lemoine, won their respective gold medal heats at the Rockshox Rotorua Pump Track Challenge ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
